      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BEAUTIFUL CHILD (5) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around this track in 34.56 to score two back then following on with a 41.62 win over 710m at this track. Flying lately and expected to go close again. SHE'S PEAKIN' (1) is drawn well on the inside. Last start finished 3rd in a Grade 5 on July 18 over 550m at Q Lakeside behind Mondo Cortez beaten 3 lengths (30.85). Can feature with the right run. HARA'S WALSH (2) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Moet Magic (41.95) in a Grade 5/6. Has the pace to be prominent. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Must be included in calculations. MIDNIGHT QUEEN (7) warrants respect following a recent placing.",
